            <h1 class="medicaltitle">特色医疗</h1>
            <div class="medicalnr">
            	                <div class="medicalone">
                    <p class="amount"><img src="/public/images/front/tsyl1.jpg" width="25" height="19" /></p>
                    <p class="amounttitle"><a href="/default/news/list/id/38">专家团队</a></p>
              </div>
                                <div class="medicalone">
                    <p class="amount"><img src="/public/images/front/tsyl2.jpg" width="25" height="19" /></p>
                    <p class="amounttitle"><a href="/default/news/list/id/39">护理团队</a></p>
              </div>
                                <div class="medicalone">
                    <p class="amount"><img src="/public/images/front/tsyl3.jpg" width="25" height="19" /></p>
                    <p class="amounttitle"><a href="/default/news/list/id/40">医技团队</a></p>
              </div>
                                <div class="medicalone">
                    <p class="amount"><img src="/public/images/front/tsyl4.jpg" width="25" height="19" /></p>
                    <p class="amounttitle"><a href="/default/news/list/id/41">特色科室</a></p>
              </div>
                                <div class="medicalinfor">
                    <p class="medicalimg">
	<img src="/public/images/front/img3.jpg" width="134" height="88" /><img src="/public/images/front/img4.jpg" width="132" height="88" /><img src="/public/images/front/img5.jpg" width="133" height="88" /> 
</p>
<p class="medicalfont">
	杭州绿康老年康复医院是经杭州市江干区卫生局批准的、是为老年残障患者提供医疗、康复、护理服务于一体的“公建民营、民办公助”、“医养结合、康复养老助残”的浙江省首家老年康复护理医疗机构；是国家民政部、中国老龄事业发展基金会“全国爱心护理工程示范基地”...
</p>
<p class="medicalmore">
	<a href="/news/detail/id/29">详情 &gt;&gt;</a> 
</p>              </div>
